1786
01:33:43.520 --> 01:33:47.799
<i>I was a lonesome cowboy</i>

1787
01:33:49.080 --> 01:33:52.198
<i>Lonesome as I could be</i>

1788
01:33:53.080 --> 01:33:57.040
<i>You came along
and changed my life</i>

1789
01:33:57.600 --> 01:34:00.672
<i>And fixed
what was broken in me</i>

1790
01:34:02.120 --> 01:34:06.956
<i>I was a lonesome cowboy</i>

1791
01:34:08.400 --> 01:34:10.437
<i>I didn't have a friend</i>

1792
01:34:11.640 --> 01:34:15.680
<i>Now I got friends
coming out of my ears</i>

1793
01:34:15.840 --> 01:34:19.516
<i>I'll never be lonesome again</i>

1794
01:34:20.720 --> 01:34:24.953
<i>You can't be happy
when you're all by yourself</i>

1795
01:34:25.120 --> 01:34:27.351
<i>Go on. tell me I'm wrong</i>

1796
01:34:27.520 --> 01:34:28.920
<i>You're wrong</i>

1797
01:34:29.480 --> 01:34:33.235
<i>When someone takes you
down from the shelf</i>

1798
01:34:33.400 --> 01:34:36.711
<i>And plays with you some
It's wonderful</i>

1799
01:34:36.880 --> 01:34:38.109
<i>Wonderful</i>

1800
01:34:38.280 --> 01:34:42.752
<i>I was a lonesome cowboy</i>

1801
01:34:44.360 --> 01:34:46.670
<i>But not anymore</i>

1802
01:34:47.840 --> 01:34:51.834
<i>I just found out
What love is about</i>

1803
01:34:52.000 --> 01:34:55.277
<i>I've never
felt this way before</i>

